<SPAN CLASS="credit">Author:</SPAN> 
<span class="credit2">Steven M. Hackett  (<a href="mailto:sillyfox@juno.com" class="credit2">sillyfox@juno.com</a>)</SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;  
<SPAN CLASS="credit">Organization:</SPAN> <a href="http://homepages.go.com/~detectivemichaelfox/main.html" class="credit2">Personal Webpage</a><br>

