<SPAN CLASS="pagesub">Must Read!  New MMORPG going Gold in July!</SPAN><br>
<img src="/images/topback.jpg" valign="bottom" width=475 height=2><br>
<SPAN CLASS="credit">Author:</SPAN> 
<span class="credit2">Savant  (<a href="mailto:SavantKnowsAll@cs.com" class="credit2">SavantKnowsAll@cs.com</a>)</SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;  
<SPAN CLASS="credit">Organization:</SPAN> <a href="" class="credit2">N/A</a><br>

<SPAN CLASS="regtext">
<!-- Begin Content -->
<P>
Today I received an Email from God.  Yes, the one and only Himself, God.  I<br>would greatly appreciate if you posted this on the main page of your site in<br>order to spread the word to all fellow gamers. With no further delay, I<br>present to you his Email to me.<br><br><BLOCKQUOTE><i>Dear Survivor(tm):<br><br>We here at Eternal Software in partnership with Heaven Productions have<br>brought to you the MMORPG known as Life for the past million years.  Life has developed at a fantastic pace, and the extensive Beta Test has gone incredibly well.  Each Beta Tester has been crucial to the development of Life.  While ups and downs have occurred, we feel that Life would not be where it is today without them.  Make no mistake, we understand that Life still has many bugs, and while they seem to be occurring on a daily basis, we have come to the conclusion that Life is not perfect.<br><br>Recently their have been rumors about Life being closed down due to lack of<br>funding and motivation.  "The Apocalypse" as it's become known by the<br>underground of the gaming community.  We assure you, this is not the case.<br>Life will continue.  On that note, I, God, bring you great news:<br><br>Life will be going Gold!  That's right, the long-awaited Full-Release of<br>Life<br>is upon us!<br><br>Life will go from a free Beta Test to a monthly fee.  While Life has no real<br>competition in its genre, we wanted to continue with the industry trend.  An<br>hourly charge was tossed around, but we've decided that in order to<br>participate in Life, beginning July 1st, each player will need to pay $9.95<br>(US Currency) per month.  This, to us, is more than fair.  We hope all who<br>stuck with us through the Beta Test will continue to participate in Life<br>Gold.<br><br>Life Gold will require NO Software!  It is completely downloadable!<br><br>Life will also open with one server to inhabit all players.  Other servers<br>will be opened depending on population boosts.  Also, as always, exploration<br>onto other Servers will occur.  Earth will remain the main server.  The Moon<br>was explored, but did not seem fitting.  Next we will attempt to open the<br>Mars Server.  (Please note that any characters made on any other server but<br>Mars will be considered to be playing on a Test Server, and may be wiped at<br>any time.)<br><br>Features in Life!<br><br>Full Player-Killing!  (We will leave it to the Morals of our players to<br>define when to and when to not PK.  While PK-Free Zones will exist, they are<br>only located in areas where the tax-bracket is above the 95% percentile.)<br><br>Countless Professions!  (All professions in Life will have a crucial effect<br>on Society! [this is however not guaranteed if you are required to wear your<br>name on your shirt in order to work])<br><br>Multiple Races!  (While some balance issues remain between the races, our<br>Head Race Guru Tiger Woods is hard at work on the issue.)<br><br>Weapons! Weapons! Weapons!  (Life will ship with a nearly unlimited supply<br>of<br>combat-oriented weapon choices!  *UPDATE*  Just Added:  Nuclear Weapons<br>[These may only be bought by those who dedicate enough time to Life to get<br>into positions of power, or by the extremely wealthy who have ties to the<br>Russian Black Market])<br><br>Skill-Based Advancement System!  (Combat is -not- required to advance in<br>Life! [unless your character happens to be born with a redneck.  Then,<br>unfortunately, a bug is apparent in the system that requires you to own a<br>shotgun and enjoy hunting])<br><br>A completely functional herbal subsystem!  (Leisure or Medical uses to be<br>discovered by the players.)<br><br>A fully operational Ecosystem!  (Tornados, Earthquakes, Floods, Natural<br>Disasters, oh my!)<br><br>NO Game Masters!  That's right, ladies and gentlemen, Life will be<br>completely<br>Game Master free.<br><br>NO Customer Support!  We here at Life feel it is up to our players to aid<br>each other.<br><br>NO Downtime Servers!  Life will have absolutely NO down time!<br><br>Eating and Sleeping are required to survive in Life.  (We felt that some<br>sort<br>of realism was crucial to be able to "be" the role, not just "play" the<br>role.<br> However, some players have been known to eventually become immune to<br>sleeping and avoid it all-together.  We do not recommend this practice.)<br><br>Life will be a Rant-Free Game!  That's right, you can rant all you want<br>about<br>Life, for absolutely NO EXTRA CHARGE!<br><br>Life will be UPDATED DAILY!   A new patch will be introduced EVERY SINGLE<br>DAY!  (However, if you live in the Midwest United States, we cannot<br>guarantee<br>much change in Life.)<br><br>The Prison System in Life is still flawed, however, rest assured that Trolls<br>will all be dealt with accordingly.<br><br>We will be releasing a patch BEFORE Life ships in order to BETTER your<br>playing experience.<br><br>Finally, Life will contain NO NERFS!  If you are born with crummy luck, WE<br>WILL NOT MAKE YOUR LIFE WORSE!  The Rich will ALWAYS remain Rich in Life!<br><br>If you have any further questions regarding Life (Or if you'd like to bug us<br>in general, give him a job in the Gaming Industry, or Host a Column/Site for<br>him) please Email SavantKnowsAll@cs.com.<br><br>Sincerely,<br><br>God</BLOCKQUOTE></I>

