[Mon Jun 26 21:23:12 2000] Logging to 'eqlog.txt' is now *ON*.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:23:30 2000] Dartain says, 'It appears that my entry back into <br>this realm has caused a bit more ...distress that I had originally <br>anticipated.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:23:58 2000] Dartain says, 'Tell me, Psalia, what do you know <br>of this individual known as Al`Kabor?'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:24:04 2000] Psalia says, 'He mentioned you expected trouble <br>from a one called Alkabor?'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:24:14 2000] Psalia says, 'Beyond that I know nothing more'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:24:33 2000] Vladde tells the guild, 'psalia hand  picked for <br>gm event in tox forest this is cool'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:24:34 2000] Players in EverQuest:<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:24:34 2000] ---------------------------<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:24:34 2000] [45 Necromancer] Psalia (Gnome) <Far Runners> <br>ZONE: tox<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:24:34 2000] There is 1 player in EverQuest.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:24:40 2000] Dartain chuckles softly as he takes a step toward <br>Psalia.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:25:11 2000] Dartain says, 'Well it appears I have already <br>made quite a powerful enemy in my re-coming to the world.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:25:13 2000] Psalia looks uncertainly at Dartain.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:25:45 2000] Dartain says, 'Unfortunately, now is not to the <br>time for me to meet this wizard and determine if he is truly a worthy <br>rival.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:26:00 2000] Dartain says, 'Coriante will be awaiting my <br>arrival.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:26:22 2000] Dartain glances Psalia over with his cold eyes, a <br>faint smirk appearing over his face.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:26:36 2000] Olafsky tells the group, 'vipin stay away from <br>him dont want to fuck this up'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:26:52 2000] Psalia says, 'Who is this Coriante?'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:27:00 2000] Dartain says, 'It has been so long since I have <br>seen the face of youth, nor met and individual who's intelligence exceeded <br>that of a pile of earth and soot.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:27:15 2000] Lorelai has gone Linkdead.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:27:19 2000] Dartain chuckles once more, his eyes lighting up <br>with amusement.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:27:30 2000] Psalia says, 'Where have you been if I might ask <br>milord?'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:27:52 2000] Dartain says, 'You have proven yourself useful, <br>Psalia. I would ask now that you continue your worth and accompany me upon <br>this meeting.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:28:03 2000] Psalia says, 'Of course.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:28:07 2000] Psalia bows before Dartain.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:28:31 2000] Dartain says, 'As well, if you have any <br>companions of which you trust dearly, then please have them brought forth as <br>well. We are in need of great experienced minds this eve.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:28:50 2000] Dartain says, 'I shall be our guide. Come.'i[Mon <br>Jun 26 21:29:35 2000] Psalia tells the guild, 'lol this is so enat'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:29:44 2000] Psalia tells the guild, 'er neat'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:31:23 2000] Dartain smiles faintly as he closes his eyes, <br>turning his face out toward the small river.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:36:12 2000] Dartain says, 'Once the Heretics found the Vault, <br>they began to experiment with it.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:37:17 2000] Dartain says, 'Inevitably, the Vault was damaged, <br>and  the denizens of the Plane of the Underfoot began to surface on  <br>Norrath.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:37:26 2000] Dartain sighs, clearly disappointed.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:37:30 2000] Leriyel tells the guild, 'I'd love to Tud, but my <br>bard is a little too low yet.  LOL'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:37:32 2000] You begin your casting.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:37:33 2000] Psalia tells the guild, 'he could be just a bit <br>more cryptic with the old lore of the world that no one knows'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:38:09 2000] Dartain says, 'A great force of elementals, lead <br>by the powerful Lord Yael, began to destroy the city of Paineel.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:38:26 2000] Dartain says, 'The Heretics were overcome, and <br>were forced to flee.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:38:53 2000] Dartain says, 'I, as well as a few others, were <br>chosen to stay behind and attempt to repair the Vault.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:39:27 2000] Dartain says, 'During that time, the others were <br>killed, be we managed to create The Hatch.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:39:56 2000] Dartain says, 'I finished the work there, but was <br>trapped in the Plane of the Underfoot, with no path back to this realm.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:40:41 2000] Dartain says, 'Recently, The Hatch was damaged <br>and the denizens escaped, as well as myself.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:41:16 2000] Dartain glances towards the hut.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:41:31 2000] Dartain says, 'Ah, the others have arrived. Let <br>us continue.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:42:30 2000] Sern Adolia bows before Dartain.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:42:32 2000] Shevra Kollintar bows before Dartain.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:42:33 2000] Coriante Verisue nods at Dartain.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:43:27 2000] Alika says, 'Psalia is Link Dead'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:44:02 2000] Dartain nods at Coriante Verisue.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:44:50 2000] Dartain says, 'I know not of these faces, <br>Coriante.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:45:06 2000] Dartain calmly motions his hand around the room.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:45:35 2000] Psalia apologizes profusely to those gathered.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:46:32 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'Sern Adolia is the Arch <br>priest within out Temple of Cazic-Thule and Shevra Killontar, a trusted <br>member of The Fell Blade, will be satnding ear for Mandaril this night'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:46:47 2000] Dartain nods at Coriante Verisue.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:46:54 2000] Dartain says, 'Very well.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:47:22 2000] Coriante Verisue raises her brow in curiosity as <br>she looks out past Dartain towards the stranger.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:47:31 2000] Dartain beams a smile at Coriante Verisue.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:47:46 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'That is a face I have no <br>recognition for'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:48:07 2000] Olafsky tells the group, 'introduce your self'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:48:08 2000] Psalia says, 'I am Dartain humble servant.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:48:12 2000] Psalia bows before Coriante Verisue.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:49:24 2000] Dartain says, 'This individual has assisted me <br>greatly these hours past. I do trust them to have an ear in this gathering. <br>Please, let us begin.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:49:31 2000] Coriante Verisue turns an icy glare upon Psalia.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:49:45 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'This should be as brief <br>as possible'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:49:51 2000] Coriante Verisue nods at Shevra Kollintar.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:49:55 2000] Shevra Kollintar nods at Coriante Verisue.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:50:27 2000] Shevra Kollintar says, 'Days have passed since <br>The Hatch, located beneath the new city of Paineel, has been tampered with'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:51:16 2000] Shevra Kollintar says, 'As you are well aware, <br>many creatures forged from earth have escaped their prison of what we <br>believe to be the Realm of the Underfoot'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:51:25 2000] Dartain says, 'Aye, your beliefs are correct, my <br>dear.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:51:58 2000] Shevra Kollintar says, 'Along with those <br>creatures, and perhaps a token of good fortune, our long lost Dartain has <br>returned.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:52:02 2000] Shevra Kollintar beams a smile at Dartain.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:52:06 2000] Dartain bows before Shevra Kollintar.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:52:11 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'Unfortunatly, milord <br>Dartain....'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:52:14 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'Your return seems to not only <br>caught our attentions.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:52:49 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'Aye, This is true. We <br>Thought we were the only ones to know of your forthcoming, but to my strong <br>suspicions, one from our very own walls leaked this information to a citizen <br>of Erudin.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:53:16 2000] Dartain cracks a half smirk and raises his brow <br>as he turns a sharp look upon Coriante.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:53:37 2000] Dartain says, 'This individual I would assume is <br>he known as Al`Kabor, yes?'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:53:42 2000] Coriante Verisue sneers coldly.<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:54:09 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'You are correct in this <br>assumption, Dartain'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:54:13 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'But that is not the only <br>reason...'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:54:15 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'why we called this meeting.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:54:53 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'Yes, Al`Kabor is but a <br>minor thorn in our boot heel as he stands alone'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:55:43 2000] Psalia tells the guild, 'sigh'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:56:17 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'The Great elemental, Lord Yael <br>who lead the raid upon our first city,...'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:57:09 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'is no where to be found within <br>the confines of the ruins, where he normally dwells.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:57:13 2000] Dartain crosses his arms over his chest, his eyes <br>quickly glancing over the room.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:57:33 2000] Dartain says, 'Yael is not one to be <br>underestimated.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:57:40 2000] Shevra Kollintar says, 'Yes, this is something we <br>are most aware of, although fortunately for us, Yael has not presented <br>himself upon the surface'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:57:54 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'Again, Yael alone is but <br>a scratch, but the might of two wizards of such power would definitely bring <br>damage to our civilization'<br>[Mon Jun 26 21:58:04 2000] Dartain says, 'Two wizards, Coriante?'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:58:30 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'Aye, Al`Kabor and the <br>infamous Yael.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:58:46 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'Not that Al'Kabor would <br>willingly befriend such a creature,...'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:59:26 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'but we do beleive that he <br>would assist it without acceptance.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 21:59:59 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'his hatred for us is stronger <br>than perhaps ours of Erudin.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:00:05 2000] Dartain nods at Sern Adolia.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:00:37 2000] Dartain says, 'What proof have you of these <br>assumptions, or are they nothing more than that, assumptions?'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:00:43 2000] Coriante Verisue raises her head proudly but <br>continues to stare coldly into Dartain's eyes.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:00:52 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'We have history as our proof, <br>milord Dartain.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:00:55 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'Please, do heed us on our <br>words, ...'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:00:58 2000] Sern Adolia says, 'we know this Al'Kabor and his <br>motions well.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:01:05 2000] Dartain nods.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:01:44 2000] Dartain says, 'I see. Have any of you ever met <br>this individual? Combated with him personally so that you would be able to <br>witness his strengths and weaknesses?'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:02:04 2000] Shevra Kollintar says, 'Nay, milord, I have not.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:02:07 2000] Coriante Verisue lowers her head forward, her <br>eyes peering out from beneath the cascade of shadow cast from her cowl.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:02:18 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'He is still alive is he <br>not?'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:02:25 2000] Dartain chuckles.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:02:47 2000] Dartain says, 'Very well. Psalia perhaps you <br>could shed some light into the arena, yes?'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:03:03 2000] Psalia says, 'I do not understand'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:03:48 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'I object! Dartain we have <br>the resources to make our own assumptions and conclusions. There is no need <br>to bring outsiders into the matter! I will not allow it!'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:04:30 2000] Dartain says, 'My dear Coriante, do not think for <br>a moment that the properties of the Underfoot would not have changed one, <br>especially over the course of two hundred years!'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:04:57 2000] Dartain glares coldy at Coriante, his eyes <br>flashing quickly to red and then back to their natural hues.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:05:06 2000] Dartain says, 'Indulge me.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:05:09 2000] Coriante Verisue Takes a deep breath removing her <br>hands from her robes as she nods gently towards Dartain.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:05:33 2000] Dartain says, 'Psalia Faute, you are one who is <br>of the world, yes?'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:05:42 2000] Psalia says, 'Yes milord'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:06:04 2000] Dartain says, 'Have you no knowledge of this one <br>they call Al`Kabor?'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:06:33 2000] Psalia says, 'My knowledge of him is very <br>limited. He seems to be a hero of.... wizards.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:07:05 2000] Dartain says, 'Ahh, I see.  I understand he is <br>from Erudin, yes?'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:07:34 2000] Psalia says, 'I believe that is so, though I have <br>never seen this wizard face to face.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:07:39 2000] Coriante Verisue says, 'Bah she is nothing but an <br>outsider'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:07:51 2000] Dartain chuckles.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:08:04 2000] Coriante Verisue shakes her head.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:08:07 2000] Anora says, 'it is not her fault that the <br>Erudites guard such knowledge from the rest of Norrath'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:08:34 2000] Dartain says, 'Aye, you know of his whereabouts?  <br>Does this puny wizard have any allies?'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:09:02 2000] Psalia says, 'I do not know of his doings.'<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:09:23 2000] Dartain nods.<br>[Mon Jun 26 22:09:41 2000] A dark messenger steps forth from the shadows, <br>his darkened features veiled in darkness.<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:10:12 2000] A dark messenger says, 'Forgive me milady, but <br>Mandaril and the rest of the Fell Blade are assembling their defenses.'<br><br>[Mon Jun 26 22:10:27 2000] A dark messenger says, 'The Elementals have begun <br>their assault upon the city walls.'<br><br>[M