<SPAN CLASS="credit">Author:</SPAN> 
<span class="credit2">Kelvin Ma   (<a href="mailto:kma@julian.uwo.ca" class="credit2">kma@julian.uwo.ca</a>)</SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;  
