eeeee!<br><br>*music*<br><br>So that dark elf did you stun you and spit in your eye!<br>He stabbed you in the back and then left you to die?<br>Ohhhh baby!<br>He did that to you baby?<br>You just got get out!<br>Just gotta get right outta Crushbone!<br><br>*music*<br><br>Nothing really matters<br>I dont lose XP<br>Nothing really matters<br>It doesnt really matter<br>At level threeeeeeee<br><br>Any way I got my corpse back....

